Description:
airDeal is an unique and authentic online shopping platform which offers consumer goods to corporate supplies, industrial goods to facilitate its country wide customers. Before delivery a product, airDeal checks it’s quality and authenticity so, it can ensure delivering 100% authentic products to customers. airDeal believes that, serving top class products to customers is very important for a sustainable business.

A number of seller offers a wide range of selected products from worldwide renowned brands with a promise of authentic, fast, safe and easy online shopping experience through airDeal.

airDeal offers a combined platform to B2B and B2C Customer at quotation system, tire pricing and retail price. Here you can buy your authentic goods for:

  -Personal Consumption at retail price;
  -Office or Business Purchase at quotation or tire pricing;

We always try to find 100% quality products to deliver our customers.

Oferecemos uma área de 1.500m² e ultrapassamos a marca de 3.000 itens em estoque para pronta entrega; Nossos materiais são estocados de maneira adequada para a conservação da qualidade dos produtos. Nossos profissionais são constantemente treinados e reciclados a fim de proporcionar a eficácia de seus serviços. Contamos com uma equipe de atendimento altamente qualificada, o que proporciona ao cliente maior agilidade e comodidade na realização de seus pedidos. Possuímos frota própria de caminhões e vans, garantindo assim o pronto atendimento.

Atendemos todos os segmentos tais como: Escolas, Indústrias, Condomínios, Padarias, Limpadoras, Clinicas E Hospitais, Gráficas, Universidades, Escritórios, Revendas, Órgão Públicos em todo território nacional.

A TEX DISTRIBUIDORA faz a diferença:
Entrega em São Paulo e Grande São Paulo em até 72 horas;
Inova continuamente em tecnologia, garantindo agilidade em suas operações;
Condições Facilitadas de Pagamento;
Atendemos empresas de pequeno, médio, grande porte, contratos corporativos, governo;
Vendas por telefone e email.

Haining Zhongfa Magnetics Co., Ltd., established in 1996, is located in Haining, Zhejiang Province, China. Zhongfa Magnetics is an ISO9001 certificated manufacturer. It has been become a leading manufacturer of high quality flexible magnetic strips/tapes and DIY magnetic insect window screen in China. 

Zhongfa is always in the pursuit of the excellence on the way of growing, now with the advanced technology and equipments, output exceeds 2 million sets of magnetic window screens and 4,000 tons of magnetic strips per year. As the competitive supplier, any related products can be customized to meet customer's different requirements to keep them enjoying diversified choices. The attitude focus on the quality has attracted more and more clients from all over the world like Germany, Italy, France, Poland, Turkey, Malaysia, USA, Canada and so on.

Our flexible magnetic strips are widely used in many fields.
1. Door edge sealing for doors, windows, sauna rooms, shower rooms; Door curtain, window wire mesh, insect screen, blinds, etc;
2. Door seals for refrigerators, freezers, wine cabinets, disinfection cabinets, medical refrigerator, thermotank, sliding door cabinets, etc;
3. Magnetic slim lightboxes, advertising printing, advertising spray painting, magnetic stickers, display boards, mesh display racks, and promotional stands;
4. Supermarket shelf label, magnetic labels, sticky notes, bulletin board label, barcode management, and warehouse inventory management, material card;
5. Stationery, educational toys, teaching aids, and office supplies;
6. Refrigerator magnet, household necessities, handicrafts, arts and crafts, paintings/awards/photos display;
7. Fixed adhesive strip for metal fasteners, tools, knives, kitchenware, tableware.

